  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onions and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and cook for another minute until fragrant.",
    "Stir in salsa verde, red pepper flakes, cumin powder, and chili powder. Cook for an additional 2 minutes to allow flavors to meld together.",
    "Pour in tomatoes (with their juice) and simmer on low heat for about 15-20 minutes or until thickened and slightly reduced.",
    "Serve hot as a main dish with injera bread."
